    "• サブスクリプションと買い切りライセンスからお選びいただけます": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "• Choose between a subscription and a one-time purchase license"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "• サブスクリプションはApple IDに請求され、期間終了の24時間以上前にキャンセルしない限り自動更新されます": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "• Subscriptions are charged to your Apple ID and renew automatically unless canceled at least 24 hours before the period ends"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "• サブスクリプションは設定アプリ > Apple ID > サブスクリプションから管理・解約できます": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "• You can manage or cancel subscriptions in Settings > Apple ID > Subscriptions"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "• 制限するアプリ／カテゴリーの個別選択\n• 休憩中の一時解除（60秒 既定）": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "• Individually select apps/categories to restrict\n• Temporary unlock during rest (60 sec default)"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "• 合計セッション: %lld": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "• Total sessions: %lld"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "• 持久力向上: 30〜45秒": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "• Endurance: 30–45 sec"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "• 期間: %@ 〜 %@": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "• Period: %@ – %@"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "new",
            "value": "• 期間: %1$@ 〜 %2$@"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "• 筋力向上目的: 2〜3分": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "• Strength: 2–3 min"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "• 筋肥大目的: 60〜90秒": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "• Hypertrophy: 60–90 sec"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "• 買い切りライセンスは一度購入すれば永久に広告なしで使用できます": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "• The one-time purchase license removes ads permanently after a single purchase"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "• 購入はApple IDに紐付けられ、同じApple IDの端末で利用できます": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "• Purchases are tied to your Apple ID and can be used on devices with the same Apple ID"
          }
        }
      }
    },
